{"title":"BCIS","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría/Orto BCIS-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"SÍNDROME DE\\NIMPLANTACIÓN DE\\NCEMENTO ÓSEO\\N(BCIS)","guid":"hqdffKEb7rapfyXQ1B_GMA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Síndrome caracterizado por **hipoxia, hipotensión y/o pérdida de conciencia**","guid":"HmekMvesXBpIm9aqCUCmTA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Ocurre durante cementación, inserción de prótesis, reducción articular o deflación de torniquete","guid":"zuULXaqFQ3jYeancrF3PQw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Descrito formalmente por Byrick → primera descripción 1970 (Powell)","guid":"mxPcS24Qle6sqKmihElG6A","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Primer uso de cemento óseo en artroplastia total de cadera → Kiaer, 1951","guid":"mj1uzMmMvl5pyyscd8_ygw","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Debate actual → revisión Bradford-Hill 2025: causalidad cemento-BCIS **no establecida definitivamente**","guid":"M3oEF3zP6LsBQ9oAi-lrrg","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"BCIS puede ocurrir **sin cemento** (embolización por manipulación femoral)","guid":"PMjyxkZ3xgIdp_ZPbf9iLQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Término “BCIS” podría ser un **misnomer**","guid":"7mTsAwNe3pK3hImAo-29sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Incidencia global artroplastias cementadas → **26%** (845/3294, Rassir 2020)","guid":"4LShkfvE-QDdV_H3tElP6g","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"**Hemiartroplastia cadera**\\N→ 28-37%","guid":"QgEEjt-4iN4m5TRjUYVbaA","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"31% (Rassir et al.)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"37% (Weingärtner et al.)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"28% (Olsen et al.)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"9","text":"Artroplastia total cadera → **24%**","guid":"wUUJHvdJEnwEQpI4_Ds5rg","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"9","text":"Artroplastia total rodilla → **28%**","guid":"MzVHL8K8Yfz4UfN2JpNSBQ","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"9","text":"Artroplastia unicompartimental rodilla → **20%**","guid":"vicwCqSwgQHbzrw17S2dbw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"9","text":"Artroplastia revisión → **23%**","guid":"okbsjw8NzH3egGDGh0Ox2w","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"9","text":"Artroplastia hombro → **16%**","guid":"eVE-3C-nCG_aMkVLPOOYag","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"9","text":"**Pacientes oncológicos** → 74% (Schwarzkopf) → **2.5x mayor** vs no oncológicos","guid":"kg9C80itvR2WOvUm3w8k-Q","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"9","text":"Mortalidad intraoperatoria ATC cementada → **0.11%** (IC 95%: 0.07-0.15)","guid":"Adwoi_Dagp-FNcW0ZSDB1g","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"9","text":"BCIS severo → mortalidad 30 días **16 veces mayor**","guid":"Ne_fIDSFQVyZZlIq7ahV4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación de Donaldson\\N(BJA 2009)","guid":"PSqkAdga2-KhlGukVq8arA","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"**Grado 1**\\N(moderado)","guid":"Uk5YVrp25zfSKxVaF12KTQ","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"SpO2 <94%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Caída PAS >20%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Mortalidad temprana 9.3% (similar a grado 0: 5.2%)","guid":"i7rPKgGPUxtn9Zn7sdzlIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"23","text":"**Grado 2**\\N(severo)","guid":"wqUtfyJn-gUMDtUwi6omow","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"SpO2 <88%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"Caída PAS >40%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"Pérdida de conciencia inesperada","guid":"K7Yjmw-i5fsnwwWIeWHEug","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"Mortalidad temprana **35%**","guid":"CaAO0sIHe7Uulp38Xsbuzg",