sis **no cementada** en pacientes alto riesgo","guid":"waICp2Wlk2UiBBct__vWnQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"136","text":"**Anestésica**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Evaluación preoperatoria exhaustiva","guid":"Oour5-JOPCy_7op4pjlIew","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"Optimización cardiopulmonar preoperatoria","guid":"mHxq7hK4_Q6QMaaFRdnOvg","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"**FiO2 0.5** durante inserción cemento (reduce desaturación)","guid":"meISwjoTOvY-JM5xJSsE1A","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"Monitoreo invasivo\\Nen alto riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"Línea arterial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"Capnografía obligatoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"Pulsioximetría continua","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"149","text":"Precarga de volumen antes de cementación","guid":"pBipGZQas189zUtHnl-2VA","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"149","text":"PAS mantener dentro de 20% valores basales","guid":"grKH7ypiXfyTAGR25TKkJQ","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"149","text":"Comunicación equipo quirúrgico → aviso antes de cementar","guid":"htAOSWIWoeXFRh9iFoxoWA","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"149","text":"Vasopresores disponibles inmediatamente","guid":"8iVsPmoy4SWXkgnDF9Lkbw","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"149","text":"Hipotensión controlada durante cementación (MAP ≤50 mmHg)","guid":"h7suzVqQ71HFCRxKsOtkzw","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"Precaución: puede empeorar si BCIS ocurre","guid":"Etarz6lLN2eVqGocEOBAUg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"136","text":"**Selección de\\Npacientes**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Alto riesgo BCIS → considerar **artroplastia no cementada**","guid":"hdCOtzq9xrxBZE3i-vVu1A","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"Ponderar riesgo BCIS vs riesgo fractura periprotésica (no cementada)","guid":"6XuM81CCgiAYRHGknG8IYQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"0","text":"Manejo Agudo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"**Soporte respiratorio**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"FiO2 100%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"Ventilación mecánica si requerida","guid":"n84PZb2_8yy1CA6ExNaC1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"**Soporte\\Nhemodinámico**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"Resucitación agresiva con fluidos","guid":"uS54eysPkdh3trjGbP21Dg","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"Vasopresores → norepinefrina primera línea","guid":"XzIhT3AQPhFolhFsdB4rrw","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"Tratamiento falla VD","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Evitar sobrecarga volumen excesiva","guid":"eluDZjcjZA44K2uHs4OOuA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Inotrópicos si shock cardiogénico","guid":"oC_6fYlmtLkCOiQhLDyfLg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"166","text":"**RCP** si paro cardíaco","guid":"","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Seguir algoritmo ACLS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Considerar embolectomía si TEP masivo","guid":"8fxC0MiskG9DuIQGpNaIYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"166","text":"**No existe tratamiento específico** → manejo sintomático y soporte vital","guid":"PEtUyiea2rF8BEA_J7trVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"0","text":"Cemento vs No\\NCemento en Anciano","guid":"","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"**WHiTE5 Trial**\\N(NEJM 2022, n=1225)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"Hemiartroplastia cementada vs no cementada moderna","guid":"uMDOKkForyos0Pd7rSrBaw","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"EQ-5D 4 meses → **0.371 vs 0. 315** (diferencia 0.055, p=0.02) → **favor cementada**","guid":"SU4NFm-9hUf-lBrr1zjJiA","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"Mortalidad 12 meses → 23.9% vs 27.8% (OR 0.80, IC 95% 0.62-1.05) → **no significativa**","guid":"sYiGNyGYB0ujyopTS5-YWA","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"181","text":"Fractura periprotésica → **0.5% vs 2.1%** (OR 4.37, IC 1.19-24.0) → **favor cementada**","guid":"y8jf4YbciR4ERWOCepAUOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"180","text":"Registro Australiano\\N(25. 000\\Nhemiartroplastias)","guid":"8H6Ne0sAcvOGgPPop7Un9Q","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"Mortalidad temprana **mayor** en cementada","guid":"QSBa7FSccMNLQVqf744w5Q","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"Diferencia disminuye con tiempo","guid":"kXqzXbfCUx1MB_6o0rm_JQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"**>80 años** → riesgo aumentado muerte con cementada","guid":"kx7iLRHT3ZfCWae42_a3Kg","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"180","text":"Registro Holandés\\N(43. 053 ATC, ≥80\\Naños)","guid":"hYZYtWvyPVd-vJFYyizJqw","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"Mortalidad **comparable** entre cementada y no cementada","guid":"JOeoq584RE_6l8lUx8YBew","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"Tasa revisión **mayor** en no cementada (HR 1.6, IC 1.4-1.8)","guid":"lgDyWliluoFoFfY8yQXYuQ","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"Fractura periprotésica → causa más frecuente revisión en no cementada","guid":"W3jrnd4ti6aIqEtJ0XAcSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"180","text":"**Consenso actual**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"Cementación preferida en fracturas cuello femoral","guid":"Qay3-m3czTVurIzXO42y_Q","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"Mejores outcomes funcionales","guid":"k_0fEu4gqpDEWHtHR7X2aw","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"194","text":"Menor tasa complicaciones implante (luxación, fractura periprotésica, revisión)","guid":"sOwt-tKmwaETghWLvEeuXg","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"194","text":"Mortalidad primer día ligeramente mayor → **se iguala con tiempo**","guid":"lxeEYj71oRvSImobdbdNrQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"194","text":"Individualizar según perfil riesgo BCIS vs fractura periprotésica","guid":"DHpLpcYry1b7tgf5zxLNwg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"0","text":"Anestesia Regional\\Nvs General","guid":"izVZC8VQt8c5Yb7MMP4zgQ","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"No diferencia significativa en mortalidad 30 días (meta-análisis)","guid":"ZQmMSBE1_AoZSxkL76AZKQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"200","text":"Anestesia regional → ↓ riesgo lesión renal aguda (meta-análisis 2022)","guid":"6bIBzuctGm1K1QMAaIjkjQ","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"200","text":"No existe técnica anestésica \"óptima\" para prevenir BCIS","guid":"_iMktfTayWDqFUPX5KX12g","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"200","text":"Agentes inhalatorios → efectos hemodinámicos más pronunciados en BCIS","guid":"gvCLL2xl5YdM_ygbn66V4A","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"200","text":"Anestesia neuroaxial podría atenuar efectos BCIS en pacientes oncológicos","guid":"ksz93BFUIKACrbszut9pww","children":[]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"0","text":"Foramen Oval\\NPermeable\\N(FOP)","guid":"k8BgWk6YDkvBdNZYO0EgSw","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"Riesgo embolia paradójica sistémica","guid":"9j88112zPbq-xsLZhCV70g","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"Considerar cierre percutáneo preoperatorio en pacientes con FOP conocido","guid":"TmAvAABAK0a3jW5k8Wj90w","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"206","text":"Caso reportado: cierre exitoso FOP previo a ATC → cirugía sin complicaciones","guid":"2UEttk9zK-UVJbsbwxcZSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"BCIS puede ocurrir SIN cemento → considerar en toda artroplastia de cadera","guid":"pf68hql2tiVBZY2-ft6wzA","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"**Lavado pulsátil es la intervención preventiva más importante**","guid":"laI6nxVbHui-gzcKaEWGJw","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"210","text":"Comunicación anestesia-cirugía ANTES de cementar → preparar vasopresores","guid":"vaX_u9oI6ID43nRzPlUafQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"210","text":"FiO2 0.5 durante cementación → reduce desaturación significativamente","guid":"R6EqWTpoKIbLOzVrOP82IQ","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"210","text":"Retrasar inserción cemento 45-60 seg después de aplicación → ↓ eventos","guid":"K1zhGBODM05heXUVGW8X7Q","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"210","text":"**BCIS grado 2-3 = emergencia vital** → RCP inmediata si colapso","guid":"EviORudAJ9oPYaqkRzdepg","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"210","text":"Paciente >80 años + ASA III-IV + EPOC → **considerar no cementada**","guid":"1tXbCV20ierrjeu7PFHj5Q","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"210","text":"Paciente con metástasis óseas → riesgo BCIS **2.5x mayor** → precaución extrema","guid":"SxEwnQzciQ8yl8Pg-IGwgQ","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"210","text":"Fractura periprotésica más común en no cementada → balancear riesgos","guid":"V_cN2ahlKI6Sr_O3DA7nfw","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"210","text":"Mortalidad cementada vs no cementada **se iguala** a mediano plazo","guid":"ioGhq73NI1BOYaps3C4EWg","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"210","text":"BCIS hipoactivo postoperatorio → puede manifestarse como **confusión/hipoxia**","guid":"5zkXKHjFXcVHQ3AZn50D7A","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"210","text":"Cemento baja viscosidad → **menor presión intramedular** (considerar en alto riesgo)","guid":"qm4AlMOR_k5pxtgOtE6BQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"1. Donaldson AJ, Thomson HE, Harper NJ, Kenny NW. Bone cement implantation syndrome. Br J Anaesth. 2009;102(1):12-22.","guid":"udhr0kBHDfAD4vnUlwB7gw","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"223","text":"2. Al-Husinat L, Jouryyeh B, Al Sharie S, et al. Bone Cement and Its Anesthetic Complications: A Narrative Review. J Clin Med. 2023;12(6):2105.","guid":"lam4c7Icv5FltkRFKbFAaQ","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"223","text":"3. Olsen F, Kotyra M, Houltz E, et al. Bone cement implantation syndrome in cemented hemiarthroplasty for femoral neck fracture: incidence, risk factors, and effect on outcome. Br J Anaesth. 2014;113(5):800-806.","guid":"Fza3BnJUcDccoG7mLMlY7w","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"223","text":"4. Weingärtner K, Störmann P, Schramm D, et al. Bone cement implantation syndrome in cemented hip hemiarthroplasty—a persistent risk. Eur J Trauma Emerg Surg. 2022;48(2):721-729.","guid":"j76CPi6F5o5cQ242A84PmA","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"223","text":"5. Bökeler U, Bühler A, Eschbach D, et al. The Influence of a Modified 3rd Generation Cementation Technique and Vaccum Mixing of Bone Cement on the BCIS in Geriatric Patients. Medicina (Kaunas). 2022;58(11):1587.","guid":"L0fP4T8iOUD1eng6ZPRMmw","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"223","text":"6. Emery RJH, Broughton NS, Desai K, et al. WHiTE 5: Cemented or Uncemented Hemiarthroplasty for Intracapsular Hip Fracture. N Engl J Med. 2022;386(6):521-530.","guid":"A1a3K7tOXSALxJTvh0pO7Q","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"223","text":"7. Chen W, Zhang W, Mu H, Song D. Study of the cement implantation syndrome: A review. Medicine (Baltimore). 2024;103(24):e38624.","guid":"7jJdZzDTvenNfjd8li47yg","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"223","text":"8. Schonhoff M, Stiehler M, Guenther KP. The cemented stem in hip arthroplasty – state of the art technique and recommendations. EFORT Open Rev. 2024; 9(11):1015-1024.","guid":"l9_6V6LAwY4ODGcdnIQ7xw","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"223","text":"9. Fu M, Shen J, Ren Z, et al. A systematic review and meta-analysis of cemented and uncemented bipolar hemiarthroplasty for femoral neck fractures. Front Med (Lausanne). 2023;10:1085485.","guid":"DUIl0HIY8GHvF4gytH8nYA","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"223","text":"10. Ryan SP, Browne JA, et al. Is Bone Cement Implantation Syndrome Actually Caused by Cement? A Systematic Review Using Bradford-Hill Criteria. J Arthroplasty. 2025;40(1):xxx.","guid":"JWmK2cxJyhPcaJE851eCIA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":233,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto BCIS-2026","id":"map_1522","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Orto BCIS-2026"}